metadata.name: Trippies Mintpass
metadata.description: Own a slice of Paradise with our collection of 10,000 unique NFTs. Inspired by BAYC #9696, Paradise was seen in Pete's trippy vision, along with the weird and wonderful creatures that lurk there. The Paradise Trippies MintPass gives you access to the Paradise Trippies pre-sale and early access to future drops by Paradise and its partners.
